into cardiac arrest.
Where's Rachel?

36:22.614 --> 36:24.581
Hey, I never thought
she was right for you, bro.

36:24.583 --> 36:25.849
What are you talking about?

36:27.252 --> 36:29.419
She's gonna be my wife.

36:29.421 --> 36:31.321
He should probably be more
concerned with his prison wife.

36:31.323 --> 36:33.190
You have the right
to remain silent.

36:33.192 --> 36:35.725
Anything you say can and
will be used against you

36:35.727 --> 36:37.194
in a court of law.
What?

36:37.196 --> 36:38.979
You have the right
to speak with an attorney...

36:38.980 --> 36:40.763
I just feel like
I'm looking in a circus mirror.

36:40.766 --> 36:43.466
Cole: Frank?

36:43.468 --> 36:44.834
Frank?

36:49.341 --> 36:50.640
It's okay.
You're okay.

36:50.642 --> 36:51.474
It's out.

36:51.476 --> 36:53.777
What about my family?

36:53.779 --> 36:54.779
Well...

36:54.780 --> 36:56.513
How are they?

36:57.783 --> 36:59.783
They're here.

36:59.785 --> 37:01.918
Pete: Dad!
Oh, God.

37:01.920 --> 37:02.953
Dad!

37:02.955 --> 37:04.487
[ Sobbing ]

37:04.489 --> 37:06.456
Karen: Frank.

37:06.458 --> 37:07.924
Frank.

37:07.926 --> 37:10.794
[ Sniffling ]
Oh, my God, you're okay.

37:10.796 --> 37:11.895
Oh.
It's okay.

37:14.233 --> 37:16.833
We're okay.

37:16.835 --> 37:18.835
We're okay.

37:18.837 --> 37:20.503
Love you, dad.

37:24.876 --> 37:27.577
You're responsible for
that picture right there, Cole.

37:29.915 --> 37:31.648
We all are.

37:44.963 --> 37:47.897
He wants to be your friend,
you know.

37:47.899 --> 37:50.967
Are you and I gonna be friends?

37:50.969 --> 37:52.669
[ Chuckles ]

37:52.671 --> 37:54.971
We're colleagues.

37:54.973 --> 37:56.906
I offended you
