they'll say yes.

38:06.018 --> 38:10.353
You ask someone out
because you are interested.

38:10.355 --> 38:12.289
And...

38:12.291 --> 38:13.523
Why are you interested?

38:15.927 --> 38:19.329
It's been a long time
since you felt someone
look at you, isn't it?

38:21.433 --> 38:22.632
Stop.

38:22.634 --> 38:24.901
Okay,
we're out of here in an hour.

38:24.903 --> 38:26.936
